# Environment Configuration Template

Copy this file to `.env.production` and fill in all values before deployment.

## CRITICAL: Security Settings

### Encryption Keys (Generate new for each environment)
```bash
# Generate with: openssl rand -base64 32
ENCRYPTION_KEY=YOUR_GENERATED_KEY_HERE
TOKEN_SECRET=YOUR_GENERATED_KEY_HERE
HASH_SALT=10
```

### API Keys (Never commit to repository)
```bash
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
API_URL=https://api.ems-guardian.medical
```

## HIPAA Compliance Configuration

```bash
# Enable HIPAA compliance mode
HIPAA_MODE=true
AUDIT_LOGGING=true
MFA_REQUIRED=true

# Data retention in days (2555 = 7 years, minimum per HIPAA)
DATA_RETENTION_DAYS=2555

# Session timeout in milliseconds (900000 = 15 minutes)
SESSION_TIMEOUT=900000

# Enable encryption
ENCRYPTION_ENABLED=true
```

## Mayo Clinic Standards Configuration

```bash
# Enable Mayo Clinic protocols and clinical validation
MAYO_PROTOCOLS=true
CLINICAL_VALIDATION=true
PROTOCOL_VALIDATION_STRICT=true
```

## Application Configuration

```bash
# Environment
NODE_ENV=production
ENVIRONMENT=production

# App settings
APP_NAME=EMS-Guardian
APP_VERSION=1.0.0
APP_URL=https://ems-guardian.medical
DEBUG=false

# Port
PORT=3000
HOST=0.0.0.0
```

## Database Configuration (if using database)

```bash
# Database connection
DB_HOST=your-database-host
DB_PORT=5432
DB_NAME=ems_guardian_prod
DB_USER=ems_guardian_user
DB_PASSWORD=strong_database_password_here

# Database encryption
DB_ENCRYPTION=true
DB_SSL=true
DB_SSL_MODE=require
```

## Monitoring & Logging Configuration

```bash
# Error tracking
ERROR_TRACKING=true
ERROR_TRACKING_KEY=your_sentry_key_here

# Performance monitoring
PERF_MONITORING=true
MONITORING_ENDPOINT=https://logs.ems-guardian.medical/api/logs

# Logging level (debug, info, warn, error)
LOG_LEVEL=info
```

## Security Headers

```bash
# CORS configuration
CORS_ORIGIN=https://ems-guardian.medical
CORS_CREDENTIALS=true

# Rate limiting (requests per minute)
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=60000
RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS=100

# API timeout in milliseconds
API_TIMEOUT=30000
RETRY_ATTEMPTS=3
```

## Email Configuration (for notifications/alerts)

```bash
# Email service
EMAIL_PROVIDER=sendgrid
EMAIL_API_KEY=your_sendgrid_key_here
EMAIL_FROM=alerts@ems-guardian.medical

# Compliance notifications
COMPLIANCE_EMAIL=compliance@ems-guardian.medical
SECURITY_EMAIL=security@ems-guardian.medical
```

## Backup & Recovery Configuration

```bash
# Backup settings
BACKUP_ENABLED=true
BACKUP_FREQUENCY=daily
BACKUP_RETENTION_DAYS=180
BACKUP_ENCRYPTION=true
BACKUP_DESTINATION=s3://ems-guardian-backups/prod/

# AWS credentials (if using S3)
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your_access_key
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your_secret_key
AWS_REGION=us-east-1
```

## Compliance & Audit Configuration

```bash
# Audit logging
AUDIT_RETENTION_DAYS=2555
AUDIT_ENCRYPTION=true

# Compliance officer contact
COMPLIANCE_OFFICER_EMAIL=compliance-officer@organization.com
COMPLIANCE_OFFICER_PHONE=+1-555-0000

# HIPAA violation threshold (severity level)
HIPAA_VIOLATION_THRESHOLD=warning
```

## Feature Flags

```bash
# Clinical features
FEATURE_ASL_TRANSLATOR=true
FEATURE_LANGUAGE_TRANSLATOR=true
FEATURE_TACTICAL_LOOKUP=true
FEATURE_VITAL_SIGNS_HUD=true
FEATURE_WEBCAM_ANALYSIS=true
FEATURE_HANDOFF_REPORTS=true
FEATURE_TRAINING_MODE=true

# Security features
FEATURE_MFA=true
FEATURE_AUDIT_LOGGING=true
FEATURE_ENCRYPTION=true
```

## Deployment Configuration

```bash
# Kubernetes/Container
CONTAINER_IMAGE_REGISTRY=your-registry.azurecr.io
CONTAINER_IMAGE=ems-guardian:1.0.0
CONTAINER_PORT=3000

# Auto-scaling (if using container orchestration)
AUTOSCALE_MIN_REPLICAS=3
AUTOSCALE_MAX_REPLICAS=10
AUTOSCALE_TARGET_CPU=70
```

## Development/Staging (Do NOT use in production)

```bash
# These should be DIFFERENT in production
ALLOW_TEST_USERS=false
ALLOW_DEMO_MODE=false
VERBOSE_LOGGING=false
SKIP_VALIDATION=false
```

---

## ⚠️ CRITICAL REMINDERS

1. **NEVER commit this file with real values to version control**
2. **NEVER share these values in Slack, email, or chat**
3. **Store in secure secret management system** (HashiCorp Vault, AWS Secrets Manager)
4. **Rotate all keys every 90 days**
5. **Different keys for each environment** (dev, staging, production)
6. **Verify all settings before production deployment**
7. **Enable MFA for production database access**
8. **Enable automated backups** with encryption
9. **Set up monitoring and alerting** for all errors
10. **Enable audit logging** for all PHI access

